reviews.review_text: Flawless service from Harpreet. She is very kind and considerate. I gave her a very complicated order that no other McDonald s was able to get right. It was perfect exactly like I wanted! Thank you very much

I don t understand why the reviews is so low for this McDonald s, they had the BEST FRIES I ever had among all the other McDonald s in Vancouver. (I even take a picture of it, I never took photos of McDonald s  ) Anyway, 100% recommend it.
Thursday, June 15 at 9:30 in the morning I came to this store and the staff was so sweet and made my breakfast bagel perfectly  Thanks ladies!

Today I was hungry and I was not sure what to eat and where to go . I end up in this McDonald and I met the most helpful McDonald staff ever.  Somaya helped me to choose the best deal and option. She was patient with me which helped me to feel less stressed. When she found out that there is no seat available and I was not happy to put my personal stuff like laptop to keep a seat available, then she offered to deliver my order to the desk. This was amazing and she is a star. I give this location manager five star for training such an amazing customer service practice. I will be back here for sure! I thought this is nice to share.

This is the best Mcdonalds branch ever. I went there to pick up my order and deliver to the customer, they surprised me and gave me a free coffee. Very friendly, professional and kind people. My special thanks to Christine and Francis for their kindness and care. I wish you all the best, prosperity, profit, health, wealth and more joy and happiness.
